To remove a package:
sudo apt --purge remove 'packagename'

Intall a package:
sudo dpkg -i *.deb

Extract a tar file:
tar -xf *.tar|tar.gz

Extract a rar file:
unrar x file.rar file_destine

browser-sync:
npm init
npm install browser-sync --save-dev
Copy this script in package:
"server-dev": "browser-sync start --server --directory --files '*.html, *.css'"

update npm:
sudo npm install -g npm

install all dependencies npm:
install i
